videos.description: Colorado's Travon McMillian breaks loose for a 64 yard run. McMillian punches it in on the next play from 3 yards out.
videos.headline: McMillian's 64-yard run sets him up for short score

videos.description: Max Borghi runs 28 yards down the sideline for a score to give Washington State a 10-7 lead over Colorado.
videos.headline: Washington St. takes lead with 28-yard score

videos.description: Gardner Minshew tosses it to Renard Bell for a 1-yard Cougars touchdown.
videos.headline: 1-yard score extends Washington State's lead

videos.description: James Williams shows off his hops by leaping over a defender in an effort to gain extra yards.
videos.headline: Cougars' Williams takes flight

videos.description: Gardner Minshew scrambles and runs for a 10-yard touchdown to give Washington State a 24-7 lead over Colorado.
videos.headline: Minshew keeps it himself for 10-yard score

videos.description: Fans love Gardner Minshew and his facial hair so much that they're starting to look like him.
videos.headline: Washington State fans love Gardner Minshew

videos.description: Colorado's Sam Noyer is initially called for targeting, but eventually overturned after his makes a questionable hit on Kedron Williams while returning an interception.
videos.headline: Colorado backup QB levels defender after INT

videos.description: Washington State QB Gardner Minshew puts a fake mustache on head coach Mike Leach after beating Colorado.
videos.headline: Mike Leach takes part in Minshew Mania
